data.description: Welcome home to beautiful Historic Ghent, with the option for VA qualified buyers to assume 3.5% VA loan! Enjoy all the established area has to offer in this impressive condo that is conveniently located only minutes from EVMS, shopping and restaurants. This 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom sizable home allows ample living space throughout. Relax and unwind with a beautiful water view of The Hague from your spacious living room and appreciate all the characteristics the 1917 unit showcases. Looking for some extra storage space? This home conveniently includes a private storage area in the basement with easy access in and out. Enjoy low-maintenance living with ground and building maintenance included in fees as well as a quaint common outdoor space. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this wonderful condo home! Some photos have been virtually staged.
